     <div class="date"> 
      <h1>52章</h1> 
      <div class="info">
       <span>作者：SISIMO</span>
       <a href="/txt16992/" title="返回《重生未来之一诺千金》介绍页" id="book16992">重生未来之一诺千金</a> 本章字节数:403794
       <script type="text/javascript">article_nav('16992','5650460');</script> 
       <a href="http://www.80txt.com/txtxz/16992.html" class="txt" id="down16992">重生未来之一诺千金txt下载</a>
